g.text: Select whether you are aiming for a "Low" score or a "High" score.
Place cards from your hand in the spaces provided.
Once all cards are placed, select "Play Hand".
(V1) Cards are played left to right.
(V2) Some special cards impact play order (read card description for more)
Your rank is based on the Total and "Low" or "High" selection
(V1) The first and last cards must be a Number Card.
(V1) 2 Operator cards cannot be placed one after another
(V1) Number cards cannot be placed one after another (in v2, players should be able to do this)
(V2) A Special Card is played on top of a Number card. They share 1 space.
A timer appears and measures how long it takes for "Player" to "Play Hand".
HardMode rounds are ranked on Total (asc for low, desc for high), then time asc
